    Method and Description
    com.pgcraft.spectatorplus.arenas.Arena.getCorner1()
    Use Arena.getLowestCorner() instead.
    com.pgcraft.spectatorplus.arenas.Arena.getCorner2()
    Use Arena.getHighestCorner() instead.
    com.pgcraft.spectatorplus.SpectateAPI.removePlayerFromArena(Player)
    Use Spectator.setArena(Arena) and pass null as argument.
    com.pgcraft.spectatorplus.SpectateAPI.setArenaForPlayer(Player, Arena)
    Use Spectator.setArena(Arena).
    com.pgcraft.spectatorplus.SpectateAPI.setArenaForPlayer(Player, Arena, boolean)
    Use Spectator.setArena(Arena).
    com.pgcraft.spectatorplus.SpectateAPI.setConfig(Object, Object, boolean)
    Use Toggles directly. This method does nothing.

    Use Arena.setCorners(Location, Location) instead.
